0few%20government%20organizations%20have%20released%0Ainformation%20about%20them%3B%20those%20that%20have%20include%20the%26nbsp%3B%3Ca%20title%3D%22Numbers%20%26amp%3B%20Oddities%20Newsletter%20%23200%22%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fnumbersoddities.nl%2FN%26amp%3BO-200.pdf%23page%3D3%22%3EPolish%0AInstitute%20of%20National%20Remembrance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20title%3D%22Numbers%20%26amp%3B%20Oddities%20Newsletter%20%23292%22%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fnumbersoddities.nl%2FN%26amp%3BO-292.pdf%23page%3D3%22%3EPolish%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3Ca%20title%3D%22Numbers%20%26amp%3B%20Oddities%20Newsletter%20%23293%22%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fnumbersoddities.nl%2FN%26amp%3BO-293.pdf%23page%3D118%22%3Earchives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%0Athe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sakerhetspolisen.se%2Fovrigt%2Fpressrum%2Faktuellt%2Faktuellt%2F2015-01-23-lyssna-pa-ett-hemligt-telegram.html%22%3E%0ASwedish%20Security%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.numbers-stations.com%2Farticles%2Frecording-instruction-numbers-stations-in-kgb-archive%2F%22%3E%0ANational%20Archives%20of%20Latvia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20number%20stations%20have%0Abeen%20involved%20in%20the%20publicly%20prosecuted%20espionage%20cases%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Fnumber-stations%2Fmorse%2Fm40%22%20title%3D%22M40%22%3EKim%20Hyon-hui%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1987)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FV%25C3%25A1clav_Jel%25C3%25ADnek%22%3EV%C3%A1clav%0AJel%C3%ADnek%3C%2Fa%3E%26nbsp%3B(1988)%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNumbers_station%23Atenci%25C3%25B3n_spy_case%22%3E%0ACuban%20Five%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1998)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAna_Montes%22%3EAna%20Montes%3C%2Fa%3E%0A(2001)%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIllegals_Program%22%3EIllegals%0AProgram%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2010)%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Fnumber-stations%2Foperators%2Frussian-7%23svr-hypothesis%22%20title%3D%22Russian%207%22%3EAndreas%20and%20Heidrun%20Anschlag%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2011).%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3ENumber%20stations%20offer%20a%20powerful%20advantage%20in%20our%20modern%20world%3A%0Apractically%20complete%20anonymity.%20The%20recipient%20of%20the%20message%20can%20be%0Aalmost%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20receive%20instructions%20without%20fear%0Aof%20being%20traced%20through%20a%20phone%20call%20or%20internet%20connection.%20All%0Athe%20recipient%20needs%20is%20a%20shortwave%20radio%20and%20to%20be%20in%20the%20right%0Aplace%20at%20the%20right%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20account%20of%20a%20number%20station%2C%20as%20reported%20in%20the%20ENIGMA%0Anewsletter%20%2312%2C%20was%20from%20an%20issue%20of%20the%20Austrian%20magazine%0A%3Cem%3EKurzwelle%20Panorama%3C%2Fem%3E%26nbsp%3Bdating%20from%20World%20War%20I.%20The%20BBC%0Awere%20noted%20for%20sending%20coded%20messages%20to%20SOE%20agents%20during%20WW2.%0AFrom%20then%20on%2C%20encrypted%20messages%20broadcast%20with%20creepy%20automated%0Avoices%20have%20appeared%20and%20disappeared%20as%20political%20events%20have%0Achanged%20over%20the%20last%2060%20years.%20Many%20number%20stations%20have%20ceased%0Aoperation%20between%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20coinciding%0Awith%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Internet%2C%20mobile%20phones%2C%20and%20cheaper%20satellite%0Acommunications.%20Conversely%2C%20since%20the%20mid%202010s%2C%20the%20activity%20of%0Aseveral%20remaining%20stations%20has%20significantly%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EENIGMA%20naming%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20number%20station%20naming%20system%20was%20devised%20by%20the%0AEuropean%20Numbers%20Information%20Gathering%20and%20Monitoring%20Assocation%0A(ENIGMA)%2C%20a%20number%20station%20research%20group%20active%20in%201993-2000%2C%20and%0Alater%20maintained%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.signalshed.com%22%3EENIGMA%0A2000%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20created%20to%20solve%20ambiguities%20in%20number%20station%0Areporting%2C%20and%20classifies%20stations%20by%20language%20or%20type%20of%20signal.%0AEach%20ENIGMA%20designator%20consists%20of%20an%20alphabetic%20prefix%20followed%20by%0Aan%20ordinary%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3ECurrent%20prefixes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EE%20-%20English%20language%20voice%20broadcasts%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3EG%20-%20German%20language%20voice%20broadcasts%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ES%20-%20Slavic%20language%20voice%20broadcasts%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3EV%20-%20Voice%20broadcasts%20in%20all%20other%20languages%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3EM%20-%20Morse%20code%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3EF%20-%20Frequency-shift%20keying%20digital%20modes%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3EP%20-%20Phase-shift%20keying%20digital%20modes%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3EXP%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Fnumber-stations%2Foperators%2Frussian-7%22%20title%3D%22Russian%207%22%3ERussian%0A7%3C%2Fa%3E%20digital%20modes%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3EHM%20-%20Hybrids%20of%20analog%20and%20digital%20modes%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EWhile%20powerful%20and%20convenient%2C%20the%20ENIGMA%20naming%20system%20isn't%0Athe%20be-all%20and%20end-all%20of%20numbers%20stations%20classification.%20There%0Ahave%20been%20other%20approaches%2C%20such%20as%20the%20predating%20practice%20of%0Anaming%20stations%20after%20their%20musical%20introduction%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%22E03%22%20href%3D%22%2Fnumber-stations%2Fenglish%2Fe03%22%3ELincolnshire%20Poacher%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%22G02%22%20href%3D%22%2Fnumber-stations%2Fgerman%2Fg02%22%3ESwedish%20Rhapsody%3C%2Fa%3E...)%20or%20just%20by%20voice%0A(English%20Man%2C%20German%20Lady)%3B%20each%20with%20their%20own%20limitations.%20The%0AENIGMA%20system%20was%20very%20useful%20in%20its%20pre-internet%20era%20of%20analog%0Aradio%20and%20distant%20community%2C%20but%20blind%20application%20in%20a%20modern%0Acontext%20with%20widespread%20digital%20tools%20might%20just%20result%20in%0Aunhelpful%20cargo%